Izap-ecommerce
------------------------

### Installation instructions

1. Grab izap-forum plugin from http://www.pluginlotto.com.
2. Uncompress downloaded folder with the name "izap-ecommerce"
3. Move that to mod.
4. Go to admin panel, find plugin and click "Activate" button.
5. Configure the plugin settings as you wish (ie. product list view, amount of discount available, 
   number of products to be viewed in a list) and here you go.

